# maybe-this-one

A dumb little hash cracker tool written in Zig.

liker jhontherripper from walmart

## Features

* Avrage Fast ( if you do -Doptimize=ReleaseFast)
* Safe ( if you do -Doptimize=ReleaseSafe)
* Tiny executable ( if you do -Doptimize=ReleaseSmall)
*  NO deps

## Supported algorithms

* MD5
* SHA-1
* SHA-256
* SHA-512
* Blake-3

More may be added later.

## Build

Requirements:

* Zig 0.16+

```bash
git clone https://github.com/khadkatulasi4321-ux/maybeThisOne

cd maybeThisOne
.
zig build -Doptimize=ReleaseFast
```

